data.title: November 22 1965 horoscope and zodiac sign meanings
data.meta_description: Here you can get all the birthday meanings for someone born under November 22 1965 horoscope explained through the astrology sign and Chinese zodiac animal.
data.text:
Do you want to get a few interesting things about November 22 1965 horoscope? Then go through the astrology profile presented below and discover facts such as Sagittarius traits, compatibilities in love and general behavior, Chinese zodiac animal properties and an assessment of personality descriptors for someone born on this day.

Horoscope and zodiac sign meanings

As a starting point here are the most often referred astrological meanings for this date and its associated sun sign:

The zodiac sign of someone born on November 22, 1965 is Sagittarius. Its dates are between November 22 and December 21.

The Archer symbolizes Sagittarius.

As numerology suggests the life path number for everybody born on 22 Nov 1965 is 9.

The polarity of this sign is positive and its observable characteristics are frank and natural, while it is by convention a masculine sign.

The element for Sagittarius is the Fire. The most important three characteristics of a native born under this element are:

being resilient when things don’t go their way

being fully engaged

having high levels of enthusiasm and energy

The associated modality for this sign is Mutable. In general people born under this modality are described by:

very flexible

likes almost every change

deals with unknown situations very well

There is a high love compatibility between Sagittarius and:

Leo

Libra

Aries

Aquarius

Someone born under Sagittarius astrology is least compatible with:

Virgo

Pisces

November 22 1965 health astrology

Someone born under Sagittarius horoscope has a predisposition to suffer from health problems in connection to the area of the upper legs, especially thighs. Below there is such a list with a few examples of illnesses and ailments a Sagittarius may confront with, but please remember that the possibility to be affected by other diseases or health issues should not be neglected:

Cirrhosis represents the condition of late stage liver disease and one of the factors to cause it is alcoholism.

Narcissistic personality disorder which is the disorder in which someone is obsessed with their own image.

Bipolar personality disorder which is characterized by seasonal changes in mood or rapid mood shifts.

Hepatitis which is the inflammation of the liver because of a viral infection with one of the five hepatic viruses.

November 22 1965 zodiac animal and other Chinese connotations

The Chinese zodiac presents a new perspective, in many cases meant to explain in a surprising way the influences of date of birth on personality and evolution of an individual's life. Within this section we will try understanding its message.

Zodiac animal details

People born on November 22 1965 are considered to be ruled by the 蛇 Snake zodiac animal.

The element connected with the Snake symbol is the Yin Wood.

It is belived that 2, 8 and 9 are lucky numbers for this zodiac animal, while 1, 6 and 7 are considered unlucky.

The lucky colors representing this Chinese sign are light yellow, red and black, while golden, white and brown are the ones to be avoided.

Chinese zodiac general characteristics

Among the properties that characterize this zodiac animal we can include:

leader person

extremely analytical person

materialistic person

dislikes rules and procedures

A few common features in love of this sign are:

jealous in nature

appreciates trust

less individualistic

likes stability

In terms of skills and characteristics that relate to the social and interpersonal side of this symbol we can conclude the following:

easily manage to attract new friend when the case

difficult to approach

has few friendships

available to help whenever the case

Few career related characteristics that may describe how this sign behaves are:

proves to adapt quickly to changes

should work on keeping own motivation over the time

often perceived as hard worker

has creativity skills
